<bridgehead class="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml:h3">ODS Feed Manager Personal Use Case:  Groups</bridgehead>
<para>A large number of discussion forums or groups provide RSS, ATOM, etc.
 links (GEMS) that allow participants to receive forum posts via feeds  These feeds may show topics from the entire group, latest discussion topics, or other selections.
 Group or forum members can click to enter the forum to participate in the discussion.
 As the topic is updated they will see new entries in the feed.</para>
